     <body>
     <div type="poem">
   <pb facs="1"/>
   <p>A SO<g ref="char:EOLunhyphen"/>VERAIGNE CORDIAL FOR a Christian Conscience.</p>
   <lg>
      <l>Content thi selfe with pacience,</l>
      <l>with Christ to bear the cros of paine</l>
      <l>which can and wil the recōpence,</l>
      <l>A thousand fold with ioyes againe</l>
      <l>Let nothīg cause thi hart to quail</l>
      <l>Laūch out thi bote, hoise vp the sail</l>
      <l>Put from the shore.</l>
      <l>And be thou sure thou shalt atain</l>
      <l>Vnto the port that shall remayne,</l>
      <l>For euermore.</l>
   </lg>
   <closer>
      <dateline>From Roane <date>the. xi. day of May Anno Domi. M. D. Liiii.</date>
      </dateline>
   </closer>
</div>
